output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. Has CMF: Yes - "Cod Mandatar Financiar Coordonator: 11240014"
2. Refers to candidate: Yes - Explicitly mentions George Simion, who is a presidential candidate (Position 2 on the ballot)
3. Addresses wide population: Yes - It's a paid advertisement with 30,000-35,000 impressions - Published on both Facebook and Instagram - Targets a large audience (100,001-500,000 people)
4. Electoral objective: Yes - Explicitly calls for votes: "Pe 24 noiembrie, votați George Simion Președinte" - Shows endorsements from multiple mayors - Clear campaign message for presidential elections
5. Journalism: No - This is clearly campaign material, not journalistic content - Contains direct call to action for voting - Presents endorsements rather than news
6. Personal opinion: No - This is a structured campaign message with endorsements - Contains official campaign financial code - Paid advertisement with clear electoral intent
This is a clear violation of Article 55 t) because: - It's active electoral propaganda for the presidential elections - The propaganda period has ended - It explicitly calls for votes for a specific presidential candidate - It's a paid advertisement with significant reach

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - Contains official campaign financial code - Direct call to vote for a specific candidate - Paid distribution for wide reach - Explicit electoral message - Uses endorsements from public officials
conclusion.message-for-police: I AM ONLINE SRL, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin difuzarea de materiale de propagandă electorală după încheierea campaniei electorale pentru alegerile prezidențiale. Postarea cu ID-ul 1324022541930513 conține un îndemn explicit de a vota candidatul George Simion la alegerile prezidențiale, fiind difuzată ca reclamă plătită pe Facebook și Instagram, cu un impact între 30.000 și 35.000 de afișări, după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Postarea include cod mandatar financiar (11240014) și reprezintă propagandă electorală conform Art. 36(7) prin prezența unui mesaj electoral explicit, identificarea clară a candidatului, și adresabilitatea către publicul larg prin natura sa de conținut sponsorizat.
